00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 14=

4
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:13,920
Your Majesty,

5
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,799
may I have my death-exemption medal now?

6
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:17,640
No.

7
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:24,159
How exactly did I offend him again?

8
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,560
What's wrong, Young Lady?

9
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,599
I'm really exhausted.

10
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,890
The rumors say
he's moody and unpredictable.

11
00:01:39,250 --> 00:01:40,599
Turns out they're completely true.

12
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,890
He changes his face faster
than turning a page.

13
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:45,040
Serving the ruler
is like serving a tiger.

14
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:49,959
(But I truly don't have much time left.)

15
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,640
Phoenix Perches Parasol,

16
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,519
Long Night Bright.

17
00:01:57,520 --> 00:02:00,239
Those two lines were the final words
of the Chifeng Army's commander.

18
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,359
How does Shen Zhinian know them?

19
00:02:05,770 --> 00:02:07,079
Shen Zhinian once mentioned to me

20
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,879
that her maternal family
lives in Chizhou.

21
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,360
Send people

22
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,759
to bring them to the capital.

23
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,680
Yes.

24
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:19,180
(Ten taels)

25
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:26,199
Why did Mother only send
a few dozen taels this time?

26
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:28,240
How is this supposed to be enough?

27
00:02:29,170 --> 00:02:30,879
Once Young Master
enters official service,

28
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,639
Eldest Young Lady, you won't
have to worry about silver anymore.

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,319
Shen Nanqiao!

30
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,120
Lu.

31
00:02:43,130 --> 00:02:45,760
Did you manage to obtain that item
at Jinsong Pavilion last night?

32
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,740
Is Duke Zhen
finally going to value you now?

33
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:48,390
Wretched woman!

34
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:50,560
Do you have any idea
how badly you've ruined me?

35
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,680
Thirteen thousand taels of silver!

36
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,190
What am I supposed to do now?

37
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:57,479
What thirteen thousand taels?

38
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:59,039
Why are you still pretending?

39
00:02:59,199 --> 00:02:59,800
Tell me.

40
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,240
Did you set me up on purpose?

41
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:04,280
From the peach tree to Jinsong Pavilion,

42
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,719
there was never any hidden master.

43
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,759
You deliberately harmed me.

44
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:08,879
No, that's not it.

45
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:09,759
Lu,

46
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,080
listen to me.

47
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,800
There really was

48
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,159
a mysterious recluse who told me.

49
00:03:15,610 --> 00:03:17,520
Otherwise, how could I possibly
have helped you

50
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,890
gain the favor of Dowager Consort Liu?

51
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,000
If I believe you again,

52
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:23,039
I'll probably end up dead
without a burial.

53
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:24,599
Lu!

54
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,479
Lu!

55
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:26,680
Don't panic.

56
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,039
What exactly happened?

57
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,879
I truly regret not chasing
after Shen Zhinian back then

58
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:31,879
and leaving with her.

59
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,560
Lu Jianglin,

60
00:03:36,180 --> 00:03:37,759
I treated you with nothing but kindness,

61
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,120
yet you resent me?

62
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,960
Shen Zhinian betrayed you,

63
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,719
and you still can't let her go.

64
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:46,840
What's so special about her?

65
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,280
Has there been any movement

66
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,000
from Duke Zhen's side?

67
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:55,990
Jiang Fu only returned
to the residence this morning.

68
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,830
Less than one hour later,
she was carried back out.

69
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,319
They say she received fifty lashes.

70
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,719
She was beaten half to death

71
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,520
and ordered to repay the silver.

72
00:04:03,090 --> 00:04:04,080
What about Lu Jianglin?

73
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,599
He went to the Duke Ding Manor,

74
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,240
but for some reason,

75
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,879
Duke Ding drove him out.

76
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,520
How strange.

77
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,439
Who exactly is Lu Jianglin working for?

78
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,000
How did he learn

79
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,400
about the Chifeng Army tally?

80
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:17,399
As long as he keeps running around,

81
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,720
he's bound to leave traces behind.

82
00:04:19,780 --> 00:04:22,279
(Tinglan Palace)

83
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:24,000
By the Mandate of Heaven,

84
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,879
the Emperor decrees.

85
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:28,079
To Shen Zhinian of the Shen family,

86
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,839
graceful and virtuous,

87
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,759
refined and dignified in conduct,

88
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,519
you are hereby
promoted to Lady of Beauty.

89
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:36,199
Respect this decree.

90
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,959
Congratulations, Lady Shen.

91
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:46,360
His Majesty already said last time that
he would promote Your Ladyship to Lady of Beauty.

92
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,120
Now the decree has finally arrived.

93
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:48,959
Come.

94
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,040
Bring the gift I prepared.

95
00:04:51,319 --> 00:04:52,520
We're going to visit Lady Liu.

96
00:04:52,530 --> 00:04:54,519
Young Lady,
why are you still bringing her gifts?

97
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,800
She nearly got you killed.

98
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:58,240
Don't forget, she saved you
in the Cold Palace.

99
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,279
What if she was the one who poisoned us?

100
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,360
It wasn't her.

101
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,399
Even if she wanted me dead,

102
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,510
she would've first investigated
my crimes thoroughly.

103
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:08,199
Besides, I'm not only visiting her
to give thanks.

104
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,079
It's also because

105
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:11,040
she's the longest serving consort
in the palace

106
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,839
aside from the Empress.

107
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,160
I want to ask her

108
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,720
about His Majesty's taboos.

109
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,000
Shen Zhinian,

110
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,600
what is the meaning of this?

111
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:25,079
I came to thank Your Ladyship.

112
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:27,040
To thank Your Ladyship

113
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,879
for saving Handan.

114
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,519
You're thanking me

115
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:31,560
with something this worthless?

116
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:35,199
I know that Your Ladyship
enjoys boundless honor and wealth.

117
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,639
Naturally, nothing is lacking.

118
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:40,439
I heard Your Ladyship
was once bold and carefree,

119
00:05:40,660 --> 00:05:41,959
and especially fond of archery.

120
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,319
So...

121
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,639
You've certainly done your research.

122
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,000
But keep your little schemes to yourself.

123
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:51,439
I stopped touching bows and arrows
after my coming of age ceremony.

124
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,759
Why care about the opinions of others?

125
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,079
If it's something
Your Ladyship truly loves,

126
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,160
why not take it up again?

127
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,720
I'm not a man.

128
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:08,079
I won't be fooled by your sweet words.

129
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:09,920
Speak.

130
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:12,319
Why exactly did you come to see me?

131
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,360
I wish to know

132
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,240
what taboos His Majesty has.

133
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:20,680
Shen Zhinian,

134
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,240
you've got some nerve.

135
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:25,399
You actually dare ask me
how to win His Majesty's favor?

136
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,079
Lives are at stake,

137
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:29,199
so I beg Your Ladyship to enlighten me.

138
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,560
I will surely
repay the favor in the future.

139
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,970
What do you mean lives are at stake?

140
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:36,720
Don't tell me you're trying
to save Lu Jianglin?

141
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,000
You still want someone like him?

142
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,519
That's not the case.

143
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,079
Then why?

144
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,680
Since you're unwilling to say,

145
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,199
I won't press further.

146
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:52,560
But if you think a single bow
will get you your answer,

147
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,879
it won't be that easy.

148
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:56,439
As long as Your Ladyship
is willing to tell me,

149
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:58,079
I would do anything.

150
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,720
I don't need you
to risk your life for me.

151
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,720
But since you've gifted me this bow,

152
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,800
I'll give you one chance.

153
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:16,240
If you can beat me,

154
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,560
I'll tell you.

155
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,199
I'll give you a handicap.

156
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,240
You go first.

157
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,800
You still have time to admit defeat.

158
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:33,279
Kowtow to me,

159
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,319
then get out.

160
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,800
Your Ladyship,

161
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,120
your turn.

162
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,759
You will personally serve as my target.

163
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,360
Your Ladyship, let me do it instead.

164
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,360
Arrows have no eyes.

165
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:39,559
Be careful,
or you may not leave here alive.

166
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,320
You still have time to admit defeat.

167
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,879
Your Ladyship,

168
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,120
please.

169
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,960
Do you know that if my arrow
misses by even an inch,

170
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:53,840
your face will be ruined?

171
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,600
Forget it.

172
00:09:11,610 --> 00:09:13,440
His Majesty's birthday banquet
is approaching.

173
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:14,840
Bloodshed would be unlucky.

174
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,200
I'll spare you today.

175
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,120
Only this once.

176
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,320
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

177
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,679
The Dowager Consort once told me

178
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,690
that when His Majesty was young...

179
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,720
If I danced in red,

180
00:09:31,730 --> 00:09:32,790
he would give me medicine.

181
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:33,559
Is that true?

182
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,279
Yes.

183
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:37,679
I always treated you as a friend.

184
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:39,960
I even risked execution to come see you.

185
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,440
And you still don't trust me?

186
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,679
His Majesty agreed.

187
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,960
He put on that shameful dance outfit.

188
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,399
Wonderful.

189
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:03,120
Dance again.

190
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,799
Dance another one. Get up.

191
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,799
Fine.

192
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,919
How boring. Let's go.

193
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,120
Give me the medicine.

194
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,000
What medicine?

195
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,720
Do you deserve it?

196
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,600
The dance ended,
but there was no medicine.

197
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,879
Only humiliation and deception.

198
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,440
So His Majesty

199
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,759
suffered so much as a child.

200
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:33,120
He's experienced too many betrayals.

201
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,790
That's why it's difficult for him
to truly trust anyone.

202
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,840
It seems I can't obtain
the death-exemption medal

203
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:41,559
through favor alone.

204
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,960
Then what will you do?

205
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:48,399
How about we
forget about the death-exemption medal?

206
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,039
Being a favored consort isn't so bad.

207
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,390
Favor is the most unreliable thing.

208
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,279
It can disappear at any moment.

209
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:57,799
Once favor is lost,

210
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,679
I can't even protect
the people around me.

211
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,960
If favor can't earn me
a death-exemption medal,

212
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:08,279
then I'll earn it with my own abilities.

213
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,000
Young Lady, you mean...

214
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,770
If I can't become a favored consort,

215
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,320
then become someone

216
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,200
who can work for him instead?

217
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:19,960
He brought me out of the palace

218
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,879
because I could help cover
for him, didn't he?

219
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:25,200
That means I can still be useful to him.

220
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,279
Make preparations.

221
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,650
I'm going to see His Majesty.

222
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,120
Your Majesty.

223
00:11:31,860 --> 00:11:32,440
Your Majesty.

224
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:33,890
Something has happened at Xunlu Pavilion.

225
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,730
Isn't the poetry competition
being held there?

226
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,970
What could've happened?

227
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:39,080
Ever since this year's
competition began,

228
00:11:39,090 --> 00:11:40,720
Lu Jianglin has always taken first place.

229
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,000
But lately, he's missed
four rounds in a row.

230
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,559
And during those same four rounds,

231
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:46,759
a brilliant scholar
from Jin suddenly appeared.

232
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,120
Every poem he composed

233
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,600
completely overwhelmed
our scholars of Daliang.

234
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,840
The poetry gathering at Xunlu Pavilion

235
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,780
was established by Your Majesty
as a path for scholars

236
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:56,520
of humble birth
to enter official service.

237
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,559
Duke Zhen

238
00:11:57,700 --> 00:11:59,960
has secretly tried to sabotage it
all along, but failed.

239
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:01,799
Yet during this gathering,

240
00:12:01,799 --> 00:12:03,559
many people from Jin suddenly appeared

241
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,919
and suppressed every scholar in Daliang.

242
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,519
A mighty nation like Daliang,

243
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,759
and between one Duke Zhen
and a few poets from Jin,

244
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:11,000
none of you can handle it?

245
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,279
Sorry to trouble you.

246
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:14,360
Please announce me.

247
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,519
Lady Shen, please enter.

248
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,279
Why are you here?

249
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:30,639
Your Majesty,

250
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:31,879
I had some free time today,

251
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,039
so I made some pastries

252
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:35,080
and brought them
for Your Majesty to try.

253
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:36,720
Just now at the door,

254
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,590
I overheard you discussing
the poetry gathering.

255
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:39,879
I humbly wish

256
00:12:40,519 --> 00:12:41,639
to give it a try.

257
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:42,960
That's right.

258
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,320
Lady Shen is exceptionally talented.

259
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,799
Those people from Jin
and Hu won't stand a chance.

260
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,200
Take this token

261
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,480
and go to Boyue Pavilion.

262
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:59,280
Review the winning essays
from previous years at Xunlu Pavilion,

263
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,790
as well as the competition rules.

264
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:02,890
I obey Your Majesty's decree.

265
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,559
Your Majesty,

266
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:10,190
are you truly allowing Lady Shen
to participate in the poetry gathering?

267
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:26,240
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

268
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:33,200
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

269
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,200
♪If we don't meet♪

270
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:40,640
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

271
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:47,360
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

272
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:54,160
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

273
00:13:54,520 --> 00:14:00,840
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

274
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:08,040
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

275
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:14,920
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

276
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:21,040
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

277
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:28,560
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

278
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:35,400
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

279
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:42,120
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

